# Spacing
- All padding / margin values ∈ {4, 8, 16, 24, 32, 40 …}.
- Use `Spacing.*` constants – never magic numbers.
- `VStack / HStack` spacing defaults:

  ```swift
  VStack(spacing: Spacing.medium) { … }
  ```

* Section separators ≥ `Spacing.large`.

